Polar Cap patches, global trans-polar coupling, sun-aligned arcs
Herb Carlson (Air Force Research Lab, USA)
Meso-scale phenomena in the polar cap (patches, reversed flow events, flow channel
propagation)
Yvonne Dabaak (U. of Oslo, Norway, and U. of Alaska, USA)
PTRANS (Patch Transit) to study decay rate for patches, large-scale changes
within patch structures
Alan Wood (Nottingham Trent U., UK)
Evolution of polar cap aurora and patches
Hanna Dahlgren (Royal Inst. of Tech, Sweden, & U. of Southampton, UK) and Joshua
Semeter (Boston U., USA)



